<br>
One thing to remember is that one of VI's favorite ways of making a tough fight tougher is to make the MOB full-MR.  They do this quite a bit and it puts wizards out of business.  I stopped even trying to follow wizard-woes back when the first lure-resistant MOB was added.<br>
<br>
I hope the additions help out wizards, but I'd definitely be wary of the end-game issues even with all the changes. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#A62A2A>- </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie>Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1>Firiona Vie General Chat</a> <font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href="http://www.firionavie.org/">Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.firiona-vie.com/fvchat.html" target="_blank"><h3>Chat Room</a></h3></center> <br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.6.2<br>Copyright ©1999-2001 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  